data.description: Newly UPDATED Garden Style Condo in Prime Smyrna Location! *EZ access to Smyrna Market Village, Truist Park, The Battery, 285/75* Spacious and Open floorplan with Dark Laminate wood style flooring thru out. Freshly painted Walls & Trim in a sought-after Decorator White paint color. Even the light switches and outlets have been upgraded to bright white.  All new trendy light fixtures thru-out with remote ceiling fans in both bedrooms. Kitchen has been updated with light granite counters, Large modern rectangular sink and new plumbing fixtures. The Dining Area opens to the spacious Family Room with Gas Fireplace. Sunroom with loads of window allows for plenty of natural sunlight and leads to the side patio.  The Primary Suite features a large walk-in closet and EZ access to the Renovated Bath with modern tiled flooring, white vanity with granite top and large walk-in shower. The secondary Bedroom has access to the side porch and makes for a great Home Office space.  Don't miss the true sized Laundry Room with full sized washer/dryer included. The HVAC has been recently replaced and there is also a pre-wired Security System. This lovely condo features a stepless entry as well which makes it perfect for pets! Assigned parking with additional guest parking right in front of unit! *FHA APPROVED COMPLEX* - Community features a Pool & Tennis courts -
